{"tid":82351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂賀]港式送火水單車 KO 蝻亞電單車","createTime":"2017-01-16T01:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T09:05:05.000Z","uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9042f37cb8154953eb0883909cdabe9c031fe14","tid":82351,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:21:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170116/56178418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170116%2F56178418&d=h5bjqPS1ZrM2LFwuuWGyz5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=02037302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170116%2F56178418&h=f56bb284\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170116/56178418</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n旺角亞皆老街近新填地街，早上6時許，一部綿羊仔電單車與一部單車相撞，兩車翻倒路中。電單車南亞裔司機與後座乘客及踏單車男子，同告墮地受傷，一併由救護員送院救治，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中電單車司機頭部重傷，送院搶救後傷重不治。現場遺下大灘鮮血</span>，由於路面濕滑並無胎痕，警方事後封閉其中3條行線，調查意外原因。<br />\n意外發生時，正下着細雨，事主駕駛綿羊仔電單車載同一名同鄉，沿亞皆老街向大角嘴方向行駛，至近新填地街對開燈位，一名送外賣男子踏單車橫過馬路。事主煞掣不及猛撞單車，繼而雙雙倒地滑行20米外，兩車3人同告墮地；其中事主因頭部纏頭巾而沒有戴頭盔，墮地後頭部重創當場昏迷，同鄉則戴有頭盔僅受輕傷，踏單車男子頭及手受傷。<br />\n本港法例規定電單車駕駛員及乘客，均需要戴上頭盔，但若有宗教信仰需要纏上頭巾或蓄有長髮綹，可以向運輸署署長申請豁免戴頭盔，亦需要向警務人員出示有關文件。"},{"pid":"46739599a3d336052de1af49d03b158663da1ba8","tid":82351,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.fungsbell.com/todaywrite/131_tobicycle/131-pic4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fungsbell.com%2Ftodaywrite%2F131_tobicycle%2F131-pic4.JPG&h=cfda6d41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99316ad929ec268f5a117db263af4794c2db8fa4","tid":82351,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"真係估唔到係電單車死"},{"pid":"2af7ed7e6b89b992a1238c2ccf94e7a626ccce67","tid":82351,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係估唔到係電單車死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過 d 咖哩開電單車係個頭得個 &quot;計&quot; 無 hamlet 死得 !"},{"pid":"ed59536f90b61fb33c01ebe0d5442f6032209207","tid":82351,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係估唔到係電單車死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地成唔帶頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dc7ec398824c207e017e333039bda0ca2ab4e9","tid":82351,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"抵   26唔用頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335873df693f2880747cf5d1f03a63da7be1725b","tid":82351,"uid":55870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"樓主早日入土為安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf5af5f86487f2cd1e091d04311bdf07f9afe54","tid":82351,"uid":23298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係估唔到係電單車死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過 d 咖哩開電單車係個頭得個 &quot;計&quot; 無 hamlet 死得 !</blockquote><br />\n哈姆雷特都救佢唔到"},{"pid":"7028500bfdb6b810f6ff524eb078f509c23b9696","tid":82351,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:37:47.000Z","msg":"其實我好細個果陣問個 d 外賣佬,火水石油汽佬<br />\n佢地同我講送貨單車前面個&quot;兜&quot;<br />\n係同元素週期表以外的金屬人手打造的....<br />\n打的時候鑄造師...會親身跳入個火爐才煉製成功 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79b747163ec3e6c7780164b21a0a9c8b8c52728","tid":82351,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2